Bongiovi:




The lasers hit Bongiovi again, instantly killing him.

"The winner, Khonkolor!" the announcer announced, the crowd leaving the 
stands to view the other matches, several soldiers approaching Khonkolor and 
a maintenance team heading to Bongiovi's body to clean it up.

"Follow us." a soldier said, all of them heading for the only exit out of the 
arena.
